---
# Session Reflect Configuration
# Copy to ~/.claude/session-reflect.local.md and customize

# Number of days to look back by default (default: 1)
default_days: 1

# Include Codex sessions in analysis (default: true)
include_codex: true

# Filter to specific projects (empty = all projects)
projects: []

# Ignore project directories matching these substrings (e.g. internal Adam test roles)
ignore_patterns: ["adam-roles"]

# Enable SessionEnd hook for auto-summaries (default: true)
auto_summary: true

# Storage directory (default: ~/.claude/session-reflect/)
storage_dir: ~/.claude/session-reflect/

# /insights facets directory for optional enrichment (default: ~/.claude/usage-data/facets/)
insights_facets_dir: ~/.claude/usage-data/facets/
---

# Session Reflect Configuration

Copy this file to `~/.claude/session-reflect.local.md` and customize the YAML values above.

Key settings:
- `default_days`: How far back /reflect looks by default
- `projects`: Filter to specific projects (empty = all)
- `auto_summary`: Whether SessionEnd hook runs automatically
- `storage_dir`: Where reflections, profile, and session tracking are stored
